{
  "title": "Diagnóstico Inicial de MAT",
  "guid": "3B72C15A0B4D92A9734CCE53",
  "filepath": "/sessions/bold-jolly-cerf/mnt/Dropbox/- Esquemas/- Entidades clínicas/General/MAT-2025-1.smmx",
  "root": {
    "id": "0",
    "parent": "-1",
    "text": "Diagnóstico\nInicial de MAT",
    "guid": "EF7doGYbzH1WCxayLpbZ2g",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "\\\\*Alto Índice de Sospecha\\\\*",
        "guid": "fIdLlAWy6VZGcg7mbahj1w",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Laboratorio Esencial\n(\\\\*Panel Inicial\\\\*):",
            "guid": "O-68fGA-Se4yy_S7Jel5EA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "3",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "\\\\*Hemograma Completo\\\\*: \nAnemia, Trombocitopenia (\\\\*<30.000/µL\\\\* en \\\\*PTT\\\\*).",
                "guid": "JfKuqQiAJMtZryimVwt26A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "4",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "\\\\*Frotis\\\\* de Sangre Periférica: \n\\\\*ESQUISTOCITOS\\\\* (≥1-2% o ≥2 por campo de alta potencia).",
                "guid": "MUD0owb-9TIYn8ItY0XivQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "5",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "Marcadores de \\\\*Hemólisis\\\\*: \n\\\\*LDH\\\\* ↑↑, \\\\*Bilirrubina Indirecta\\\\* ↑, \\\\*Haptoglobina\\\\* ↓↓ (o indetectable), \\\\*Reticulocitos\\\\* ↑.",
                "guid": "WAhwzSi-em92zTyxYZyz2g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "6",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "Prueba de \\\\*Coombs Directa\\\\* \\\\*Negativa\\\\* (Diferencia de AHAI).",
                "guid": "eDf9aGeu3qwlhSWlAyRBvA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "7",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "Estudios de \\\\*Coagulación\\\\*:  \\\\*TP\\\\*, \\\\*TTPa\\\\*, \\\\*Fibrinógeno\\\\*, \\\\*Dímero-D\\\\*.\n(Normales PTT/SHU vs. MUY alterados en \\\\*CID\\\\*).",
                "guid": "Y94TUFy6ZcMeb2OwRikUcQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "8",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "\\\\*Función Renal\\\\*:  BUN, Creatinina.",
                "guid": "afq8k2hRX34D3840ZoIIKA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "9",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "\\\\*Actividad\nADAMTS13\\\\*",
            "guid": "CMTM-V80VrlBzuY-bKLgSQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "10",
                "parent": "9",
                "text": "\\\\*< 10%: Confirma PTT\\\\*.",
                "guid": "bgRI1EpR3RpUKmv_K2bV6A",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "11",
                    "parent": "10",
                    "text": "\\\\*Ac anti-ADAMTS13 positivo\\\\*",
                    "guid": "CBZE6w1BtXAfW-6TLgjzlA",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "12",
                        "parent": "11",
                        "text": "\\\\* PTT Adquirida.\\\\*",
                        "guid": "AP2gCmCV7Tdh-sgpCRPk9Q",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "13",
                "parent": "9",
                "text": "≥ 10%: \\\\*PTT Improbable\\\\*.",
                "guid": "AAoMax20LKoqSLGcWBJ9OQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "14",
                    "parent": "13",
                    "text": "Investigar \\\\*otras causas\\\\* de MAT \n(SHU, CID, HTA Maligna, fármacos, neoplasia, etc.).",
                    "guid": "RnKnGSEV7k05rzETPqqkgQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "MAT en >60a \nBúsqueda de Causas Secundarias",
        "guid": "WeVvsXTk_V5SfleaIFgWyg",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "16",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "1. Malignidad",
            "guid": "a2HfZyDRoYkLYpjuJ1Cb4w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "17",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "Adenocarcinomas (GI, pulmón, mama, próstata), neoplasias hematológicas.\nA menudo ocultas.",
                "guid": "dNpQmVmllisAM4cmddfwow",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "18",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "Evaluación:",
                "guid": "OjuDY2IuT1B-69WYKBMmCw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "19",
                    "parent": "18",
                    "text": "Anamnesis dirigida \n(Síntomas B, baja de peso, cambios hábito intestinal, etc.).",
                    "guid": "Y4UGDDYIriIrrKLuXebUAg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "20",
                    "parent": "18",
                    "text": "Examen físico completo \n(adenopatías, masas, tacto rectal).",
                    "guid": "cjnxKXZI7rBYUq5kTB9g2g",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "21",
                    "parent": "18",
                    "text": "Estudios de Imagen: TAC Tórax-Abdomen-Pelvis c/cte.",
                    "guid": "ay3sDirRBf5sd3ekASjXug",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "22",
                    "parent": "18",
                    "text": "Endoscopías / Marcadores Tumorales: Según sospecha clínica.",
                    "guid": "Nv6OrEt6MvAf6JBfImBuEw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "23",
                    "parent": "18",
                    "text": "Biopsia Médula Ósea: Si citopenias adicionales, hallazgos en frotis o sospecha.",
                    "guid": "bEvUeStLKU1JsQn3bVu_8Q",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "24",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "2. Infecciones",
            "guid": "aXm29xbrHuo2-1TWXlQHkA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "25",
                "parent": "24",
                "text": "Presentaciones atípicas/oligosintomáticas.\nSepsis puede gatillar CID con HAMA.",
                "guid": "cJC1Fjcu2_1UK_gzKsw4eQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "26",
                "parent": "24",
                "text": "Evaluación:",
                "guid": "GV0rTVMXzctS316EfOIxWQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "27",
                    "parent": "26",
                    "text": "Hemocultivos seriados.",
                    "guid": "CSB77n6MAXJayQVce1ptFw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "28",
                    "parent": "26",
                    "text": "Serología VIH.",
                    "guid": "dNTwIzMbs8BHec3yYALcMQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "29",
                    "parent": "26",
                    "text": "Otras según contexto: CMV, VHB, VHC, Influenza, urocultivo.\nNeumococo asociado a SHU.",
                    "guid": "Xey5vjPxRZZhK7PrFOtIaw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "30",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "MAT en >60a \nBúsqueda de Causas Secundarias",
        "guid": "HaO9NHORWkdN3hwWbnPyXQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "31",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "1. Malignidad\n(Neoplasias)",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "32",
                "parent": "31",
                "text": "Adenocarcinomas (GI, pulmón, mama, próstata), neoplasias hematológicas.\nA menudo ocultas.",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "33",
                "parent": "31",
                "text": "Evaluación:",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "34",
                    "parent": "33",
                    "text": "Anamnesis dirigida (Síntomas B, baja de peso, cambios hábito intestinal, etc.).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "35",
                    "parent": "33",
                    "text": "Examen físico completo (adenopatías, masas, tacto rectal).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "36",
                    "parent": "33",
                    "text": "Estudios de Imagen: TAC Tórax-Abdomen-Pelvis c/cte.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "37",
                    "parent": "33",
                    "text": "Endoscopías / Marcadores Tumorales: Según sospecha clínica.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "38",
                    "parent": "33",
                    "text": "Biopsia Médula Ósea: Si citopenias adicionales, hallazgos en frotis o sospecha.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "39",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "2. Infecciones",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "40",
                "parent": "39",
                "text": "Presentaciones atípicas/oligosintomáticas.\nSepsis puede gatillar CID con HAMA.",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "41",
                "parent": "39",
                "text": "Evaluación:",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "42",
                    "parent": "41",
                    "text": "Hemocultivos seriados.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "43",
                    "parent": "41",
                    "text": "Serología VIH.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "44",
                    "parent": "41",
                    "text": "Otras según contexto: CMV, VHB, VHC, Influenza, urocultivo.\nNeumococo asociado a SHU.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "45",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "3. Enfermedades\nAutoinmunes:",
            "guid": "FXLVlW68R-hseSt7UclgNw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "46",
                "parent": "45",
                "text": "Debut tardío de LES, SAF, Esclerosis Sistémica.",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "47",
                "parent": "45",
                "text": "Evaluación",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "48",
                    "parent": "47",
                    "text": "ANA, Anti-DNA, ENA.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "49",
                    "parent": "47",
                    "text": "Complemento (C3, C4): Bajos en LES activo.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "50",
                    "parent": "47",
                    "text": "Anticoagulante Lúpico, Anti-Cardiolipinas (IgG/IgM),\nAnti-Beta2 Glicoproteína I (IgG/IgM).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "51",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "4. Fármacos",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "52",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Revisión\nexhaustiva",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "53",
                    "parent": "52",
                    "text": "Prescritos, OTC, suplementos, herbales\nInicio reciente y uso crónico.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "54",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Fármacos Comunes\nAsociados a MAT:",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "55",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "Quimioterápicos (Mitomicina C, Gemcitabina, Cisplatino).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "56",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "Inmunosupresores / Biológicos (Ciclosporina, Tacrolimus, Interferón, Bevacizumab).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "57",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "Antiagregantes (Clopidogrel, Ticlopidina).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "58",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "Antibióticos (Quinina, Penicilinas).",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "59",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Suspender fármacos sospechosos y monitorizar evolución clínica y de laboratorio.",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "60",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "5. Hipertensión Arterial Maligna /\nEmergencia Hipertensiva",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "61",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "PA >180/120 mmHg + Daño agudo órgano blanco\n(LRA, encefalopatía, IC, retinopatía grado III/IV).",
                "guid": "",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "62",
            "parent": "30",
            "text": "6. Estudios Dirigidos a SHU \n(si ADAMTS13 ≥10% y LRA prominente)",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "63",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "SHU",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "64",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "Diarrea (sanguinolenta) reciente, brote comunitario, contacto con ganado.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "65",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "Detección de Toxina Shiga en deposiciones (ELISA/PCR) y/o cultivo\npara E. coli O157:H7 / productora de Shiga.",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "66",
                "parent": "62",
                "text": "aSHU",
                "guid": "fhr2hQMUvBYP-qNCVYIhJw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "67",
                    "parent": "66",
                    "text": "Puede haber historia familiar o personal de eventos trombóticos/renales.",
                    "guid": "e5SxdGtdjWEvpXTzNDJhRg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "68",
                    "parent": "66",
                    "text": "Niveles C3, C4, CH50 (Normalidad no lo descarta).\nEstudios genéticos / Ac anti-FH",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
